<ce:table colsep="0" frame="topbot" id="t0035" rowsep="0" xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/cals/dtd">
<ce:label>Table 5</ce:label>
<ce:caption>
<ce:simple-para id="sp130" view="all">Catalytic oxidation of styrene with <ce:bold>1</ce:bold>.</ce:simple-para>
</ce:caption>
<tgroup cols="9">
<colspec align="left" colname="col1"></colspec>
<colspec align="left" colname="col2"></colspec>

<colspec align="left" colname="col4"></colspec>

<colspec align="char" char="." colname="col8"></colspec>
<colspec align="char" char="." colname="col9"></colspec>
<thead>
<row rowsep="1" valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<bold>1</bold> (μmol)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Solvent</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Styrene (mmol)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Oxidant (mmol)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Time (h)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<italic>T</italic> (°C)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">t.o.n.</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Conversion (%)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Epoxide (%)</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<bold>1</bold>
</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">2</inf>Cl<inf loc="post">2</inf>
<cross-ref refid="tblfn1">
<sup loc="post">a</sup>
</cross-ref>
</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0.5</entry>

<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">6</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">20</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">450</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">90</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">83</entry>
</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<bold>1</bold>
</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Acetone<cross-ref refid="tblfn2">
<sup loc="post">b</sup>
</cross-ref>
</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0.5</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">H<inf loc="post">2</inf>O<inf loc="post">2</inf> (5)</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">4</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">170</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">34</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">59</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
<ce:table-footnote id="tblfn1">
<ce:label>a</ce:label>
<ce:note-para>5<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>mL.</ce:note-para>
</ce:table-footnote>
<ce:table-footnote id="tblfn2">
<ce:label>b</ce:label>
<ce:note-para>1<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>mL. t.o.n.<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>=<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>converted mol/mol metal catalyst.</ce:note-para>
</ce:table-footnote>
</ce:table>

<ce:table colsep="0" frame="topbot" id="t0040" rowsep="0" xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/cals/dtd">
<ce:label>Table 6</ce:label>
<ce:caption>
<ce:simple-para id="sp140" view="all">Oxidation of alkenes with <ce:italic>m</ce:italic>-CPBA catalyzed by <ce:bold>1</ce:bold>, at 0<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>°C.</ce:simple-para>
</ce:caption>
<tgroup cols="4">
<colspec align="left" colname="col1"></colspec>
<colspec align="left" colname="col2"></colspec>
<colspec align="left" colname="col3"></colspec>
<colspec align="char" char="." colname="col4"></colspec>
<thead>
<row rowsep="1" valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Alkene</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Solvent</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Time (h)</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Conversion (%)</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row valign="top">
<entry morerows="1" xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Styrene</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">2</inf>Cl<inf loc="post">2</inf>
</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">5</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">67</entry>
</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">3</inf>CN</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">3</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">95</entry>
</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<italic>Cis</italic>-stylbene</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">3</inf>CN</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">3</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">94</entry>
</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Cyclohexene</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">3</inf>CN</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">≪1<cross-ref refid="tblfn3">
<sup loc="post">a</sup>
</cross-ref>
</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">99</entry>
</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
<italic>Trans</italic>-4-octene</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">CH<inf loc="post">3</inf>CN</entry>
<entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">≪1<cross-ref refid="tblfn3">
<sup loc="post">a</sup>
</cross-ref>
</entry>
<entry align="char" char="." xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">98</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
<ce:legend>
<ce:simple-para id="sp155" view="all">Reaction conditions: alkene (0.5<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>mmol), catalyst (20<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>μmol), <ce:italic>m</ce:italic>-CPBA (1<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>mmol), solvent (1<ce:hsp sp="0.25"></ce:hsp>mL).</ce:simple-para>
</ce:legend>
<ce:table-footnote id="tblfn3">
<ce:label>a</ce:label>
<ce:note-para>The first aliquot taken a few minutes after the reaction started showed maximal conversion.</ce:note-para>
</ce:table-footnote>
</ce:table>
clean_text:
Table 6. Oxidation of alkenes with m-CPBA catalyzed by 1, at 0°C.

| Alkene        | Solvent | Time (h) | Conversion (%) |
|---------------|---------|----------|-----------------|
| Styrene       | CH2Cl2  | 5        | 67              |
|               |         |          |                 |
| CH3CN         | 3       |          | 95              |
| Cis-stylbene  | CH3CN   | 3        | 94              |
| Cyclohexene   | CH3CN   | ≪1[^a]   | 99              |
| Trans-4-octene| CH3CN   | ≪1[^a]   | 98              |

[^a]: The first aliquot taken a few minutes after the reaction started showed maximal conversion.

Reaction conditions: alkene (0.5mmol), catalyst (20μmol), m-CPBA (1mmol), solvent (1mL).
